      • guid

        private java.lang.String guid
        Unique identifier for the project. If an iterator is defined for this project, it will be altered such that we are able to distinguish between the different versions of the project.

        See Constant.Navigation, createProjects(ArrayList, DataContext) and fillWithAcquiredData()

        public void checkValidity()

        This method is intended to be called after the full application content has been built.
